# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Competitive Intelligence Pipeline — Environment Variables
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# Copy to .env and fill in your keys:
#   cp .env.example .env

# NVIDIA NIM (free tier)
# Get your key at: https://build.nvidia.com/
NVIDIA_API_KEY=nvapi-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
NVIDIA_BASE_URL=https://integrate.api.nvidia.com/v1
NVIDIA_MODEL=meta/llama-3.1-70b-instruct

# Tavily Search (free tier)
# Get your key at: https://tavily.com/
TAVILY_API_KEY=tvly-xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# Slack Integration (optional)
# Webhook URL for notifications after analysis completes
# Get your webhook at: https://api.slack.com/messaging/webhooks
# Leave empty to disable Slack notifications
SLACK_WEBHOOK_URL=

# ChromaDB (Docker internal)
CHROMA_HOST=chromadb
CHROMA_PORT=8000

# Logging
LOG_LEVEL=INFO
